  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### Request audit contract\nEvery `litellm_request` span becomes one log line in the Loki stream `{service_name=\"aigw-requests\"}`. Each line carries `aigw.user.id`, `aigw.project.id`, `aigw.api_key.id` (SHA-256 fingerprint only), `aigw.request.id`, the model/token/cost fields, and the approved `gen_ai.input.messages` / `gen_ai.output.messages` content; `| logfmt` exposes them as `aigw_user_id`-style fields (Logs Drilldown filters work the same way). Raw authorization, API keys, request headers, email, IP, and unfiltered LiteLLM auth metadata are removed before any export. Prompt content is sensitive and this dashboard is intentionally ADM-only.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.5",
      "title": "How to inspect a request",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.5",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (aigw_user_id) (count_over_time({service_name=\"aigw-requests\"} | logfmt [$__auto]))",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Requests by User",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "currencyUSD"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
